title: Zendaya Goes Undercover on YouTube, Twitter and Wikipedia | GQ
author: GQ
description:
On this episode of Actually Me, February cover star Zendaya goes undercover on the Internet and responds to real comments from YouTube, Twitter, Instagram, Quora, IMDb and Wikipedia. Who is her favorite Harry Potter character? Does she have any tips on dealing with stress and anxiety?

Check out Zendaya's new film "Malcolm & Marie" out February 5th on Netflix.
